
Overview of adv secretly

The adv secretly has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (3) secretly, in secret, on the Q.T., on the QT -- (in secrecy; not openly; "met secretly to discuss the invasion plans"; "the children secretly went to the movies when they were supposed to be at the library"; "they arranged to meet in secret")
2. (1) secretly -- (not openly; inwardly; "they were secretly delighted at his embarrassment"; "hoped secretly she would change her mind")
